maple: A100994 := proc(n) if nops(numtheory[factorset](n)) <> 1 then 1 ; else n ; fi ; end: A014963 := proc(n) if nops(numtheory[factorset](n)) <> 1 then 1 ; else op(1,op(1,ifactors(n)[2])) ; fi ; end: A134579 := proc(n) local e ; e := A014963(n)*A100994(n)-n ; if e >= 0 then n^e ; else 0 ; fi ; end: seq(A134579(n),n=1..13) ; # _R.
